works.description: We have showcased rare Ferrari’s going under the hammer in our coverage, such as the 1955 Ferrari 375 MM Berlinetta by Pinin Farina which has been auctioned off recently and the 1958 S412, which sold for $8 million. The latest to go under the hammer is the 1952 Ferrari 340, of which only three exist in today’s times. With multiple accolades and participation records to its name, this matching numbers’ Ferrari will be one of the most special models at the auction in California later this year.
